      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WALTER WARLOCK (9) was a beaten favourite last start but was forced to work when caught wide so it may pay to be forgiving. Owns a good record at this circuit and distance and draws for a trail. With his A-game he can win if he gets the gaps. LOVE LOU (10) is another drawn on the back row but he will find this easier than recent attempts at Menangle. Won the last time he raced here and with even luck he has the ability to find the winners' list. SPIRIT KING (4) is hard to knock having recorded two wins and two placings from his last four outings at this circuit and distance. Respect. YESNOMAYBESO (1) has been coming from the back row of late and producing some good efforts including a win at this circuit and distance two back. Won the last time he started on the front line so include from the inside draw.",
